      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_037",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_037.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊，啊呃！这里，很舒服！呼啊……嗯，",
        "哈啊！好刺激！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "刚才的痛苦表情已经明显减轻了。",
        "不仅如此，她的感觉比我想象的还要强烈。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「怎么样？绫姐……感觉舒服吗？」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "我自己也感受到了快感，试着问了一下。",
        "然后姐姐连连点头，告诉我她正在享受着。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_038",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_038.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「虽然处女膜破裂的地方有些刺痛，但这里却有一种让人心醉神迷的感觉……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "每次姐姐动一下，都会擦到肉棒的顶端。",
        "这种感觉太过舒服，声音不由自主地溢出来。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_039",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_039.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯……这，这样真好……啊啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "似乎很高兴，绫姐一次又一次地擦着小穴。",
        "她不仅能让我感到舒服，自己也能享受其中。",
        "对于姐姐来说，这可谓一举两得。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_040",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_040.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯，这样继续下去，嗯嗯！",
        "力量，都消失了……啊啊，呼啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "绫姐发出了有些焦虑的声音。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_041",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_041.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「好像要尿出来了，呼啊……啊呜，嗯嗯！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "感觉很舒服，力气都没了吗。",
        "如果姐姐在和我做爱时感受到了快感，我会非常高兴。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_042",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_042.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「还有其他地方很舒服……嗯啊，呼啊，我要找找看……嗯嗯，呼呼！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "绫姐重新深深地坐下。",
        "我的肉棒再次深入她的阴道，龟头牢牢地抵达最深处。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_043",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_043.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊，嗯嗯，嗯嗯！呼啊，这也很舒服……呜呜，呼啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "看来已经不那么痛苦了，她稳稳地用力，磨擦到最深处。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_044",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_044.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯，啊啊……！感觉像是抬起了肚子，或许我喜欢这种感觉……咕，呼啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "绫姐这样说着，顶住了肉棒的龟头，往子宫深处推进。",
        "像是吸附在龟头上的感觉，是子宫口吗？"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_045",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_045.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「感觉被填满了……嗯嗯，啊啊！",
        "有种放松的感觉！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "这样深入连接在一起，阴道内的感觉也逐渐变化。",
        "爱液的量也增加了，整个阴道都湿润而黏腻地缠绕着。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H002A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h002a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_046",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_046.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼啊……咕嗯！嗯嗯，啊哈！",
        "嗯嗯，啊啊……肉棒好厉害！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "姐姐的腰使力量越来越强。",
        "紧紧地包裹着肉棒，摩擦着。",
        "仿佛绫姐的身体在向我索求射精。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_047",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_047.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯，呼啊……！啊，啊啊，好厉害！",
        "嗯，啊啊！往深处，往深处顶进去！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "姐姐的动作越来越激烈。",
        "我的肉棒被猛烈地插入和抽出。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_048",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_048.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊！嗯，嗯咕噜！哈，哈！",
        "啊啊，好厉害……那里，啊啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "真的好舒服到肉棒都要融化了。",
        "在这种快感中，如果能射精就太爽了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「绫姐，差不多要射了……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "我坦率地说道，姐姐俯视着我说：「嗯嗯，随时都可以射进来哦！"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "想什么时候射就射吧！」",
        "她这样说着，更加用力地动着腰。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・微笑み・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_06"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_050",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_050.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「随时都可以射进来哦！尽情地在我里面射吧！想要噗噗地射精！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8101C",
          "file": "se/8101c.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "可能是因为听到了我的射精声音，绫姐的腰动得更加剧烈了。",
        "阴道紧紧地收缩着，刺激也越来越强烈。",
        "起初的时候，感觉肉棒一直顶击着深处。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_051",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_051.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊，啊呃！好舒服，太好了，啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "但现在感觉肉棒一直紧贴着，仿佛被姐姐的子宫深处吞没。",
        "每当她的腰上下摆动，像是在拉扯着肉棒。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_052",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_052.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊呜，嗯嗯！好厉害，啊！啊呜！",
        "深处一直有幸福的感觉呢！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "绫姐全神贯注地动着腰。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_053",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_053.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯！啊，呼啊！喜欢，喜欢你！",
        "啊啊呜！我爱你！啊啊，咕啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "仿佛整个阴道都在对待我的肉棒，或者说仿佛在阴道中吮吸着。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊……要出来了，要出来了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_054",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_054.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「射出来！射得多一点！啊啊啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "姐姐一边说着，一边更用力地扭动着腰。",
        "肉棒的顶端深深地插入最深处。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN006C_055",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan006C_055.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊嗯！贴紧最深处，射得多一点点！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "被紧紧地夹住，同时感觉像是被挤压着。",
        "伴随着这个感觉，我射精了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV018・うっとり・挿入後・破瓜",
        "file": "EV018_07"
      },
      "se": [
        {
